I hope this email finds you well.

=20

Below are corporate and operations training opportunities for you and your =
organization, available both in person at Concorde Hotel, Kuala Lumpur, Mal=
aysia, and virtually via Zoom video conference.

=20

Topic 1 - Human + AI Productivity Tools [8 - 9 April 2026]

The Human+AI Productivity Tools workshop is a practical, hands-on 2-day pro=
gram designed to help professionals integrate AI into their daily work in a=
 structured, responsible, and highly productive way. Participants will expl=
ore how Human+AI collaboration can enhance communication, planning, researc=
h, documentation, and decision-making =97 while ensuring human oversight, c=
ritical thinking, and professional judgement remain central to every proces=
s.

=20

Topic 2 - Organizational Design & Development for Middle Managers [13 - 14 =
April 2026]

This workshop equips middle managers and senior supervisors with a practica=
l understanding of organizational design and development, focusing on how s=
tructure, roles, processes, culture, and performance systems align to suppo=
rt strategy execution. Participants will explore key organizational design =
principles, common structural challenges, and modern organizational models,=
 enabling them to identify misalignment that affects efficiency, accountabi=
lity, and collaboration.

=20

Topic 3 - Building Organizational Culture & Transformation [4 - 5 May 2026]

This two-day program, Building Organizational Culture & Transformation, is =
designed for middle and senior managers, transformation leads, and high-pot=
ential leaders who want to turn culture into a strategic advantage. Partici=
pants will explore the fundamentals of organizational culture, diagnose cur=
rent cultural realities, and understand how culture directly impacts strate=
gy execution, performance, and employee behavior.

=20

Feel free to request brochures for more information.

=20

On the other hand, if you wish to not receive further emails such as this, =
simply put the word =93remove=94 on the subject and send back to us. Thank =
you.

=20

=20

Best regards,

Mark


